sequenceDiagram
    participant MLModel as ML Model/Inference Service
    participant OnlineService as Online Feature Server<br/>6566/TCP HTTP or 6567/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant RegistryService as Registry Server<br/>6570/TCP gRPC or 6572/TCP HTTP
    participant OnlineStore as Online Store<br/>(Redis/Cassandra/DynamoDB)
    participant OIDCProvider as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3

    Note over MLModel,OnlineStore: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval for Inference

    MLModel->>OnlineService: POST /get-online-features<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OIDC) or K8s RBAC

    alt OIDC Authentication
        OnlineService->>OIDCProvider: Validate JWT Token<br/>HTTPS/443
        OIDCProvider-->>OnlineService: Token Valid
    else Kubernetes RBAC
        OnlineService->>OnlineService: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Check feast.dev permissions
    end

    OnlineService->>RegistryService: Fetch Feature Metadata<br/>gRPC or HTTP
    RegistryService-->>OnlineService: Feature Schema & Config

    OnlineService->>OnlineStore: Query Features<br/>Native Protocol, TLS 1.2+<br/>DB Credentials
    OnlineStore-->>OnlineService: Feature Values

    OnlineService-->>MLModel: JSON Response<br/>Feature Vector

    Note over MLModel,OnlineStore: Flow 2: Historical Feature Retrieval for Training

    participant Notebook as Jupyter Notebook
    participant OfflineService as Offline Feature Server<br/>8815/TCP HTTP or 8816/TCP HTTPS
    participant OfflineStore as Offline Store<br/>(S3/GCS/Snowflake)

    Notebook->>OfflineService: POST /get-historical-features<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OIDC) or K8s RBAC

    alt OIDC Authentication
        OfflineService->>OIDCProvider: Validate JWT Token<br/>HTTPS/443
        OIDCProvider-->>OfflineService: Token Valid
    end

    OfflineService->>RegistryService: Fetch Feature Metadata<br/>HTTP or gRPC
    RegistryService-->>OfflineService: Feature Schema & Config

    OfflineService->>OfflineStore: Query Historical Data<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Cloud IAM/Credentials
    OfflineStore-->>OfflineService: Historical Feature Dataset

    OfflineService-->>Notebook: JSON/Parquet Response<br/>Training Dataset

    Note over MLModel,OnlineStore: Flow 3: Feature Materialization (Offline → Online)

    participant CronJob as Materialization CronJob

    CronJob->>RegistryService: Fetch Feature Definitions<br/>HTTP or gRPC
    RegistryService-->>CronJob: Feature List & Config

    CronJob->>OfflineService: Request Latest Features<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    OfflineService->>OfflineStore: Query Latest Data<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    OfflineStore-->>OfflineService: Latest Features
    OfflineService-->>CronJob: Feature Data

    CronJob->>OnlineService: POST /push<br/>Push Features to Online Store
    OnlineService->>OnlineStore: Write Features<br/>Native Protocol, TLS 1.2+
    OnlineStore-->>OnlineService: Write Confirmed
    OnlineService-->>CronJob: Success Response
